<document>

  <properties>
    <title>Common Modules</title>
  </properties>

  <body>
    <section name="Common modules">
      <p>Mevenide IDE plug-ins rely on a few common non-UI modules:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="../mevenide-core/index.html">Mevenide Core</a>
          provides POM management support. It can be used to read, write
          and modify a project's model.
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="../goals-grabber/index.html">Mevenide Goals Grabber</a>
          provides access to a project's Maven goals and reports.
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="../mevenide-config/index.html">Mevenide Config</a>
          provides an API for resolving environment related properties
          and variables.
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="../mevenide-grammar/index.html">Mevenide Grammar</a>
          provides an API for retrieving code completion proposals.
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="../mevenide-repository/index.html">Mevenide Repository</a>
          provides Maven repository browsing support for both local and
          remote repositories.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </body>

</document>